### POMS Backend — Manual API tests
### VS Code: ติดตั้ง extension `humao.rest-client` แล้วกด "Send Request" เหนือแต่ละ block
### IntelliJ/WebStorm: รองรับ native (HTTP Client)

@host = http://localhost:3000
@apiPrefix = /api/v1

###############################################################################
# 1. Health check
###############################################################################

### Health
GET {{host}}/health

###############################################################################
# 2. Login flows (3 user types)
###############################################################################

### 2.1 Login — Admin officer (วีกิจ ชมญาติ)
# @name loginAdmin
POST {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userType": "officer",
  "username": "weekit",
  "departmentID": "2",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

### 2.2 Login — KPM officer (เจ้าหน้าที่ กฝม.)
# @name loginKpm
POST {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userType": "officer",
  "username": "officer_kpm",
  "departmentID": "2",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

### 2.3 Login — Provincial officer (สอจ. สระบุรี)
# @name loginProvincial
POST {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userType": "officer",
  "username": "officer_sng",
  "departmentID": "2",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

### 2.4 Login — Operator (ธนาภรณ์ — 2 บริษัท + 7 โรงงาน)
# @name loginOperator
POST {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userType": "operator",
  "citizenId": "3191000135709",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

### 2.5 Login — Citizen
# @name loginCitizen
POST {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userType": "citizen",
  "username": "citizen_demo",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

###############################################################################
# 3. /me — ดู profile ของตัวเอง (ต้อง login ข้อ 2.1 ก่อน)
###############################################################################

### 3.1 /me ด้วย admin token
GET {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{loginAdmin.response.body.data.accessToken}}

### 3.2 /me ด้วย operator token
GET {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{loginOperator.response.body.data.accessToken}}

###############################################################################
# 4. Error cases (ทดสอบ error handling)
###############################################################################

### 4.1 Wrong password → 401 UNAUTHORIZED
POST {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userType": "officer",
  "username": "weekit",
  "departmentID": "2",
  "password": "WRONG"
}

### 4.2 Missing password → 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
POST {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userType": "officer",
  "username": "weekit",
  "departmentID": "2"
}

### 4.3 Operator without citizenId → 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
POST {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userType": "operator",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

### 4.4 Invalid userType → 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
POST {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userType": "robot",
  "username": "hack",
  "departmentID": "2",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

### 4.5 No Authorization header → 401
GET {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/auth/me

### 4.6 Invalid Bearer token → 401
GET {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer fake.token.value

### 4.7 Unknown route → 404
GET {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/does-not-exist

###############################################################################
# 5. Non-existent user
###############################################################################

### 5.1 Officer ที่ไม่มีใน fixtures → 401
POST {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userType": "officer",
  "username": "ghost_user",
  "departmentID": "2",
  "password": "demo1234"
}

### 5.2 citizenId รูปแบบผิด → 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
POST {{host}}{{apiPrefix}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userType": "operator",
  "citizenId": "abc",
  "password": "demo1234"
}
